{"data":[{"name":"113:1","price":"1਼ (ਹੇ ਨਬੀ!) ਤੁਸੀਂ ਆਖੋ ਕਿ ਮੈਂ ਸਵੇਰੇ ਦੇ ਰੱਬ ਦੀ ਸ਼ਰਨ ਵਿਚ ਆਉਂਦਾ ਹਾਂ।","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"2਼ ਹਰੇਕ ਉਸ ਚੀਜ਼ ਦੀ ਬੁਰਾਈ ਤੋਂ (ਬਚਣ ਲਈ) ਜਿਹੜੀ ਉਸ ਨੇ ਪੈਦਾ ਕੀਤੀ ਹੈ।","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"3਼ ਅਤੇ ਹਨੇਰੀ ਰਾਤ ਦੀ ਬੁਰਾਈ ਤੋਂ ਜਦੋਂ ਉਹ ਛਾ ਜਾਂਦੀ ਹੈ।","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"4਼ ਅਤੇ ਗੰਢਾਂ ਵਿਚ ਫੂਕਾਂ ਮਾਰਨ ਵਾਲਿਆਂ ਦੀ ਬੁਰਾਈ ਤੋਂ।","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the knots","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","al-nafāthāti","fī","al-ʿuqadi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2150],[3,2150,4440],[4,4440,4630],[5,4630,5935]]}},{"name":"113:5","price":"5਼ ਅਤੇ ਈਰਖਾ ਰੱਖਣ ਵਾਲਿਆਂ ਦੀ ਬੁਰਾਈ ਤੋਂ ਬਚਣ ਲਈ ਜਦੋਂ ਉਹ ਈਰਖਾ ਕਰੇ।","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ حَاسِدٍ إِذَا حَسَدَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6230,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ḥāsidin idhā ḥasada ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) an envier","when","he envies","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ḥāsidin","idhā","ḥasada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1990],[3,1990,3160],[4,3160,3750],[5,3750,5605]]}},{"name":"114:1","price":"1਼ (ਹੇ ਨਬੀ!) ਆਖ ਦਿਓ ਕਿ ਮੈਂ ਮਨੁੱਖਾਂ ਦੇ ਰੱਬ ਦੀ ਸ਼ਰਨ ਵਿਚ ਆਉਂਦਾ ਹਾਂ।","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6231,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-nāsi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) mankind","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,330],[2,330,1230],[3,1230,2050],[4,2050,6085]]}},{"name":"114:2","price":"2਼ ਸਾਰੇ ਮਨੁੱਖਾਂ ਦੇ ਪਾਤਸ਼ਾਹ ਦੀ (ਸ਼ਰਨ ਵਿਚ)।1","arabic":"مَلِكِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6232,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1 ਅੱਲਾਹ ਦੇ ਰਸੂਲ (ਸ:) ਨੇ ਫ਼ਰਮਾਇਆ, ਅੱਲਾਹ ਕਿਆਮਤ ਵਾਲੇ ਦਿਨ ਧਰਤੀ ਨੂੰ ਆਪਣੀ ਮੁੱਠੀ ਵਿਚ ਲਵੇਗਾ ਅਤੇ ਅਕਾਸ਼ਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਆਪਣੇ ਸੱਜੇ ਹੱਥ ਵਿਚ ਲਪੇਟ ਲਵੇਗਾ। ਫਿਰ ਫ਼ਰਮਾਏਗਾ, ਮੈਂ ਬਾਦਸ਼ਾਹ ਹਾਂ, ਧਰਤੀ ਦੇ ਬਾਦਸ਼ਾਹ ਕਿੱਥੇ ਹਨ ? (ਸਹੀ ਬੁਖ਼ਾਰੀ, ਹਦੀਸ: 7382","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"maliki al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) King","(of) mankind","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["maliki","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,5205]]}},{"name":"114:3","price":"3਼ ਅਤੇ ਸਾਰੇ ਮਨੁੱਖਾਂ ਦੇ ਇਸ਼ਟ (ਅੱਲਾਹ) ਦੀ (ਸ਼ਰਨ ਵਿਚ ਆਉਂਦਾ ਹਾਂ)।","arabic":"إِلَٰهِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6233,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"ilāhi al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) God","(of) mankind","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ilāhi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,5295]]}},{"name":"114:4","price":"4਼ ਉਸ ਭਰਮ ਭੁਲੇਖਾ ਪਾਉਣ ਵਾਲੇ ਸ਼ੈਤਾਨ ਦੀ ਬੁਰਾਈ ਤੋਂ (ਬਚਣ ਲਈ), ਜਿਹੜਾ (ਅੱਲਾਹ ਦਾ ਨਾਂ ਸੁਣਦੇ ਹੀ) ਭੱਜ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ। 2","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ ٱلۡوَسۡوَاسِ ٱلۡخَنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6234,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2 ਇਸ ਤੋਂ ਭਾਵ ਸ਼ੈਤਾਨ ਹੈ ਤੇ ਇਸ ਦਾ ਭਾਵ ਮਨੁੱਖੀ ਇੱਛਾਵਾਂ ਵੀ ਹਨ ਕਿਉਂ ਜੋ ਉਹ ਵੀ ਮਨੁੱਖ ਨੂੰ ਆਮ ਕਰਕੇ ਬੁਰਾਈ ਵੱਲ ਹੀ ਲੈਕੇ ਜਾਂਦੀਆਂ ਹਨ ਜਿਵੇਂ ਕਿ ਹਦੀਸ ਵਿਚ ਹੈ, ਅੱਲਾਹ ਦੇ ਰਸੂਲ (ਸ:) ਨੇ ਫ਼ਰਮਾਇਆ ਕਿ ਨਰਕ ਮਨੁੱਖੀ ਇੱਛਾਵਾਂ ਵਿਚ ਘਿਰੀ ਹੋਈ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ ਜੰਨਤ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਕੰਮਾਂ ਵਿਚ ਘਿਰੀ ਹੋਈ ਹੈ ਜਿਹੜੀ ਦਿਲ ਨੂੰ ਬੁਰੀਆਂ ਲੱਗਦੀਆਂ ਹਨ। (ਸਹੀ ਬੁਖ਼ਾਰੀ, ਹਦੀਸ: 6487) ● ਇਸ ਤੋਂ ਭਾਵ ਹੈ ਕਿ ਮਨੁੱਖੀ ਇੱਛਾਵਾਂ ਤੇ ਰੁਵਾਨੀ ਜਜ਼ਬਾਤ ਨਰਕ ਵੱਲ ਹੀ ਅਗਵਾਈ ਕਰਦੇ ਹਨ ਜਦ ਕਿ ਇੱਛਾਵਾਂ ’ਤੇ ਕਾਬੂ ਪਾਉਣਾ ਪਵਿੱਤਰਤਾ ਧਾਰਨ ਕਰਨਾ, ਨੇਕੀ ਦੇ ਦੂਜੇ ਕੰਮ ਤੇ ਅੱਲਾਹ ਅਤੇ ਉਸ ਦੇ ਰਸੂਲ ਦੀ ਤਾਬੇਦਾਰੀ ਜੰਨਤ ਵੱਲ ਲੈਕੇ ਜਾਂਦੀ ਹੈ। ਜਿਹੜੀਆਂ ਕਰਤੂਤਾਂ ਨਰਕ ਦਾ ਕਾਰਨ ਬਣਦੀਆਂ ਹਨ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਦਾ ਕਰਨਾ ਬਹੁਤ ਸੌੌਖਾ ਦਿੱਸਦਾ ਹੈ ਜਦ ਕਿ ਜੰਨਤ ਦੀ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤੀ ਵਾਲੇ ਕੰਮ ਔੌਖੇ ਵਿਖਾਈ ਦਿੰਦੇ ਹਨ।","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri al-waswāsi al-khanāsi ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) the whisperer","the one who withdraws","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","al-waswāsi","al-khanāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2119],[3,2119,3389],[4,3389,7914]]}},{"name":"114:5","price":"5਼ ਜਿਹੜਾ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦੇ ਮਨਾਂ ਵਿਚ ਭਰਮ ਭੁਲੇਖੇ ਪਾਉਂਦਾ ਹੈ।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُوَسۡوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6235,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yuwaswisu fī ṣudūri al-nāsi ","translations":["The one who","whispers","in","(the) breasts","(of) mankind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yuwaswisu","fī","ṣudūri","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2130],[3,2130,2510],[4,2510,3420],[5,3420,7865]]}},{"name":"114:6","price":"6਼ ਉਹ ਭਾਵੇਂ ਜਿੰਨਾਂ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ ਹੋਵੇ ਜਾਂ ਮਨੁੱਖਾਂ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ।","arabic":"مِنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6236,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-jinati wal-nāsi ","translations":["From","the jinn","and men","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-jinati","wal-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2610],[3,2610,8185]]}}],"dua":{"id":4,"name":"Dua for Protection","arabicName":"دعاء الحماية","reference":"113:1-5, 114:1-6","verseTitle":"The Protection and Refuge Supplication","significanceReason":"Powerful duas seeking protection from negative energies, evil intentions, and spiritual harm. Considered a shield against potential dangers."},"version":{"key":"punjabi_arif","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"pa","version":"1.0.0","last_update":1666783255,"title":"Punjabi translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Punjabi by Arif Halim, published by Darussalam"}}